  <brief_title>Comparative Assessment of Adjuvant Effect of Cultured Epidermal Autografts Versus Skin Allografts on Wound Healing of Burns Treated With Widely Expanded Skin Autograft Using Meek Micrografting Technique MEEKADEAU</brief_title>
  <acronym>MEEKADEAU</acronym>
  <official_title>Comparative Assessment of Adjuvant Effect of Cultured Epidermal Autografts Versus Skin Allografts on Wound Healing of Burns Treated With Widely Expanded Skin Autograft Using Meek Micrografting Technique MEEKADEAU</official_title>
